reviewText: My three year old daughter loves Dora. The 'mermaid kingdom' episode is probably her favorite. You get two movies for basically the price of one! Very happy to own these episodes on DVD.
Great buy, my daughter loves them...
My daughters love it. Now that they don't the original Dora's on the TV anymore, it was definitely a great buy!

My daughter's favorite version of Dora is when she is a mermaid so this DVD collection was right up her alley.  It features Dora as a mermaid as well as some other great water-related episodes.  You get a total of six episodes and two music videos jam packed into this set.  I will say they are episodes your child may have seen already on television but for us it was great to have them on hand in one set.  It is perfect for any Dora fan or mermaid fan!

Dora the Explorer: Mermaid Adventures Collection Includes:

DISC 1 - Dora Saves the Mermaids
Dora Saves The Mermaids
Fish Out Of Water
Treasure Island

Bonus Features:
Clean-Up Song Music Video
Yo Gabba Gabba! Music Video

DISC 2  Doras Rescue in Mermaid Kingdom
Doras Rescue in Mermaid Kingdom
Benny the Castaway
Doras Moonlight Adventure
